<?xml version='1.0' encoding='UTF-8'?>
<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id7a912f33-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8934"><num value="8934">§ 8934.</num><heading> Data usage</heading><subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id7a912f34-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8934/a"><num value="a" class="bold">(a)</num><heading class="bold"> In general</heading><chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Director shall provide the sampling data collected under <ref href="/us/usc/t15/s8933">section 8933 of this title</ref> to—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7a912f35-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8934/a/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> the Administrator; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="id7a912f36-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8934/a/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> other Federal and State regulatory agencies on request.</content>
</paragraph>
</subsection>
<subsection style="-uslm-lc:I19" class="indent2 firstIndent-2" id="id7a912f37-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0" identifier="/us/usc/t15/s8934/b"><num value="b" class="bold">(b)</num><heading class="bold"> Usage</heading><content><p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The sampling data provided under subsection (a) shall be used to inform and enhance assessments of exposure, likely health and environmental impacts, and remediation priorities.</p>
</content>
</subsection>
<sourceCredit id="id7a912f38-552d-11f1-9071-ff305b7c3ff0">(<ref href="/us/pl/116/92/dF/tLXXIII/s7334">Pub. L. 116–92, div. F, title LXXIII, § 7334</ref>, <date date="2019-12-20">Dec. 20, 2019</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/133/2283">133 Stat. 2283</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
